<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62d90b26-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s4307"><num value="4307">§ 4307.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as are necessary to carry out this chapter, to remain available until expended.</p>
